# ESP-IDF sdkconfig generated files
sdkconfig*

# Web frontend source lives in web-src/. data/www is generated publish output.
# Keep tracked gzip/static assets when release artifacts are intentionally updated,
# but ignore raw generated copies and stale split-module directories.
data/www/**/*.html
data/www/**/*.js
data/www/**/*.css
data/www/js/modules/device-control/
data/www/js/modules/protocol/
